snippet.title: Neopunk Trailer - Open World Cyberpunk Retro RPG
snippet.description:
Start a new life in a cyberpunk world. Freedom awaits you in Neopunk. Solve a murder. Buy apartments. Deliver pizza. Who will you be? Currently in development for release in Q1 2023. Preorder now and support development on Kickstarter!

https://www.kickstarter.com/projects/solohack3r/neopunk-open-world-cyberpunk-retro-rpg
https://solohack3r.itch.io/neopunk

Music by Karl Casey @ White Bat Audio.
